  "summary": "Parent brand typography: H1 Avenir Black Title Case Dark Blue #262262/Purple #92278F; H2 Avenir Black sentence case Dark Blue/Purple; Body Avenir Roman sentence case Black #000000; ISI subheads Avenir Black ALL CAPS Black; Footnotes Avenir Book sentence case Black; Campaign headline Avenir Black ALL CAPS campaign palette; Callouts Avenir Black ALL CAPS."
